          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/888138-suzanne?shelf=spiritual">spiritual</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer14901431" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7712721995816302063">Read this in college when most of it went over my head...then life happens. After a life full of joy and tragedy and senseless loss at times...this work sits in my nightstand drawer so I can be renewed, reawakened and reminded of higher purposes when the world is too much with me.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

