        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2971197508" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2842526561775110906">I already thought Lewis&apos;s wisdom and analytical mind was amazing before I read <i>The Four Loves</i>. Now that I have read it, I&apos;m convinced saying merely <i>that</i> would be a gross understatement. He weaves analogy like a magician and makes logic an art form, and through it all has helped me begin to understand the concept of love in all its forms and nuances. Most importantly, he has awakened in me anew a desire to aspire to the Love that is God Himself. Thank you, God, for the gift Lewis is to the world.</span>
  <span id="freeText2842526561775110906" style="display:none">I already thought Lewis's wisdom and analytical mind was amazing before I read <i>The Four Loves</i>. Now that I have read it, I'm convinced saying merely <i>that</i> would be a gross understatement. He weaves analogy like a magician and makes logic an art form, and through it all has helped me begin to understand the concept of love in all its forms and nuances. Most importantly, he has awakened in me anew a desire to aspire to the Love that is God Himself. Thank you, God, for the gift Lewis is to the world.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2842526561775110906" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


