        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/973558-shiloah?shelf=personal-theme-audio">personal-theme-audio</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/973558-shiloah?shelf=spiritual">spiritual</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/973558-shiloah?shelf=personal-theme-inspires-greatness">personal-theme-inspires-greatness</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/973558-shiloah?shelf=world-british-isles">world-british-isles</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/973558-shiloah?shelf=adult-non-fiction">adult-non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/973558-shiloah?shelf=novella">novella</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/973558-shiloah?shelf=british-lit">british-lit</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/973558-shiloah?shelf=family-marriage">family-marriage</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/973558-shiloah?shelf=genre-relationships">genre-relationships</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/973558-shiloah?shelf=classic-theater">classic-theater</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1127354907" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16798674598242890484">A book I think should be read more widely. I<br/>appreciated Lewis&apos;s insights.<br/><br/>2019 reading- Lewis felt that he didn’t know a book until he read it at least 2-3 times. I’m seeing how true this is. I barely remembered what I read from 5 years ago. This book is even more insightful this time around as I’m a different person. His views on friendship were on par for me. I have many underlinings in my book. I plan to revisit this one again—sooner than later.</span>
  <span id="freeText16798674598242890484" style="display:none">A book I think should be read more widely. I<br />appreciated Lewis's insights.<br /><br />2019 reading- Lewis felt that he didn’t know a book until he read it at least 2-3 times. I’m seeing how true this is. I barely remembered what I read from 5 years ago. This book is even more insightful this time around as I’m a different person. His views on friendship were on par for me. I have many underlinings in my book. I plan to revisit this one again—sooner than later.</span>
